title: Myths of the World Stolen Spring Collectors Edition-Wendy99

::::::: WENDY99 PRESENTS :::::::


:::: Myths of the World Stolen Spring Collectors Edition-Wendy99 ::::


Genre: Adventure | Hidden Object | Puzzle


The rich folklore continues with this exciting tale set in an old Slavic land. 
As Child of Spring, can you save the world from eternal winter? A cruel and cold Goddess of Winter has hijacked springtime, and her victim has called on you for help. You'll be surprised by what you, a lowly peasant, can do in the face of 
evil and what cute little furry friends you'll meet along the way in Myths of 
the World: Stolen Spring.


This is a special Collector's Edition release full of exclusive extras You won't find in the standard version.
